summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from C. B. Dodge Co., a corporation to the City of Seattle, dated the 13th day of May, 1908, to certain portions of land in Block two (2) and in "A" St. (now vocated) Maynard's Lake Washington Addition to Seattle and in Block three (3) Lakewood Addition, a replat of part of Maynard's Lake Washington Addition to Seattle.
